    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Warding. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: choose one of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.zGrUu3dUtqHrqGuo]{Break Curse}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.MSyU208twPGKU16W]{Calm and Centered}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.MMaUL7r99DY7nvds]{Comforting Presence}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Occultism checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.TC7OcDa7JlWbqMaN]{Treat Disease}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.KjoCEEmPGTeFE4hh]{Treat Poison}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.1kGNdIIhuglAjIp9]{Treat Wounds}. At 17th level, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
